### Endpoint: Vincular Pictogramas ao Paciente (Múltiplos)
### URL: http://localhost:8000/api/patient/{patient_id}/pictograms/

# ====================
# TESTES PARA VINCULAÇÃO DE PICTOGRAMAS
# ====================

# ATENÇÃO: 
# - O endpoint agora suporta tanto vinculação única quanto múltipla
# - Para um pictograma: use o campo "pictogram"
# - Para múltiplos pictogramas: use o campo "pictograms" (array)

### 1. Teste com um único pictograma (comportamento original)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/patient/1/pictograms/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "pictogram": 1
}

### 2. Teste com múltiplos pictogramas
POST http://localhost:8000/api/patient/1/pictograms/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "pictograms": [2, 3, 4, 5]
}

### 3. Teste com dois pictogramas apenas
POST http://localhost:8000/api/patient/1/pictograms/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "pictograms": [6, 7]
}

### 4. Teste com pictogramas duplicados (deve falhar)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/patient/1/pictograms/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "pictograms": [1, 2, 1, 3]
}

### 5. Teste com pictograma já vinculado (deve falhar)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/patient/1/pictograms/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "pictograms": [1, 8]
}

### 6. Teste com array vazio (deve falhar)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/patient/1/pictograms/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "pictograms": []
}

### 7. Teste sem pictogram nem pictograms (deve falhar)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/patient/1/pictograms/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
}

### 8. Teste com pictogram ID inválido (deve falhar)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/patient/1/pictograms/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "pictograms": [999, 1000]
}

# ====================
# ENDPOINTS RELACIONADOS
# ====================

### Listar pictogramas do paciente
GET http://localhost:8000/api/patient/1/pictograms/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Desvincular pictograma do paciente
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/patient/1/pictograms/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar pictogramas disponíveis para vincular
GET http://localhost:8000/api/patient/1/available-pictograms/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
